<h1 id='language'>Language</h1>
<p>The language drop-down menu lets you switch languages.</p>

<p><img src="/images/img/language-drop-down-menu.png" alt="language-drop-down-menu" /></p>

<p>Ten languages are currently supported. More language will follow.</p>

<p>Anyone wishing to help with translations can <a href="https://github.com/xaya/xaya_electron/tree/master/src/assets/i18n">find the language resources at the 
open source Github respository 
here</a>.</p>
